---
import Layout from '../layouts/Page.astro';
import HeroCards from '../components/HeroCards.astro';

const title = 'Welcome';
const description = '';
const section = 'home';
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} section={section}>
  <HeroCards />

  <p>This is a template for building a simple blog website with the <a href="https://astro.build">Astro</a>, with deployment to <a href="https://www.netlify.com">Netlify</a>.</p>

  <p>Includes <a href="https://www.netlifycms.org">Netlify CMS</a> for WYSIWYG content editing, and <a href="https://www.netlify.com/docs/form-handling">Netlify Forms</a> for processing your site's form data.</p>

  <p>For more info on installation and usage, view the <a href="https://github.com/navillus-bv/demo-astro-netlify-cms">project repo</a> on GitHub.</p>

  <p>Or click the button below to deploy your own copy of this project to Netlify.</p>

  <a href="https://app.netlify.com/start/deploy?repository=https://github.com/navillus-bv/demo-astro-netlify-cms&stack=cms">
    <img src="https://www.netlify.com/img/deploy/button.svg" alt="Deploy to Netlify" />
  </a>
</Layout> 